{"tid":2430681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜清唱《小幸運》寵粉！開直播自爆是「香菜控」","createTime":"2021-03-03T05:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:31:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4348daa190e6049f2fd87b082f45a3fa1b0fd6a","tid":2430681,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/03/03/phpvFwH5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F03%2F03%2FphpvFwH5e.png&h=2f4f010c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜還大方開放粉絲截圖蒐藏可愛萌照。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓女團TWICE台灣成員周子瑜，時常和粉絲分享日常生活，1日更開直播和粉絲炫耀自己新買的帽子，寵粉的她還用中文清唱《小幸運》，融化大批粉絲。其中最令人驚訝的是，子瑜在直播過程中更自爆是個「香菜控」，立刻掀起一番熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/03/03/php1Fcnf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F03%2F03%2Fphp1Fcnf4.png&h=618edcca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜近日開直播和粉絲互動，還清唱《小幸運》寵粉。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜在1日開直播和粉絲互動，還大方放送截圖時間，她對著鏡頭wink撒嬌，模樣超萌。過程中她竟自爆是香菜控，並用中文回覆留言，還讓媽媽寄了很多泡麵給她，透露很喜歡台灣的乾麵。最後，她更加碼用中文甜美清唱《小幸運》，融化全場粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n直播影片曝光後，不少粉絲紛紛激動留言，「子瑜唱歌很好聽阿」、「清唱都能這樣了，看誰嘲說她沒實力」、「很多人低估她的唱歌實力了」。還有不少人稱讚她直播的可愛模樣，大讚素顏還能這麼美，直呼：「真是特寫女王！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RvHDT68hIOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRvHDT68hIOU&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiun8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=bd82a247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RvHDT68hIOU</a>"},{"pid":"b97210cbe8d669e1f3f8a4cb1eeb1ee8b69d1d0c","tid":2430681,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"共諜唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a046a819f640772046adc3aa9745b8d2ef0429","tid":2430681,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1